# hn / host net
host + site snapshot

## structure
```
hostnet/
├── setup.ps1         master script
└── scripts/
    ├── 0.ps1         sanitize
    ├── 1.ps1         snapshot
    └── 2.ps1         host + config
```

## requirements
pulls in everything it needs on its own
- Windows
- PowerShell
- XAMPP — auto-installs if not found
- HTTrack — auto-installs if not found

## scripts
individual scripts can also be run standalone

|setup.ps1|
|-|
|installs what it needs, runs what it has to, no setup required|
```ps1
irm https://is.gd/hsetup | iex
```

|sanitize.ps1|
|-|
|removes the site, cleans hosts + vhosts|
```ps1
irm https://is.gd/hreset | iex
```

